data.description: $5,000 BUYER CREDIT FOR CLOSING/RATE BUY-DOWN!  Discover the charm of this delightful 2 bed, 1 bath home located close to downtown Emmett. With a new shed, enclosed utility room and flex area that boosts tons of storage. The kitchen showcases stainless appliances perfect for preparing meals and entertaining. Master bedroom has a large walk in closet for even more storage!  Step outside to a great backyard, offering endless possibilities for outdoor activities and relaxation listening to the backyard rock stream. Full auto sprinklers to water the beautiful outdoor retreat and garden area just past the back fence. New water heater (2024) & New ductless mini split for heat and a/c (2021), Whether you're a first-time buyer or looking to downsize, this house offers a perfect blend of modern updates and a fantastic location.
